column3: “Nice nuggets real og gangsta weed, i smoked this and my mind was like jänkäjonko. I took hits from the kingokongo, it was spantterspasting.”

“Being an extremely active person as well as anxious, White Skunk has been a saviour to my mind and nerves. I am functionally relaxed and really enjoy the natural, orange creamsicle aroma and flavor.”
“This one is really nice for pain. It is for me anyway, Instant relief.”

“I love my White Skunk Concentrate. the taste is mild, the smoke is clear. 
The way I feel though, sleepy, relaxed, it's wonderful to nut hurt tonight..”

“found some white skunk with 2.7 cbd and 20 thcc its a high ceiling and a cerebral at first. didnt notice any sleepiness even at high doses which is nice.. the smell isnt super strong but complex with orange citrus/pine/skunk odor. when I first opened the jar it was reallllyyy nice smelling like earthy skunk berry. its a pretty heavy effect but only after you moke alot, which I reccomend”

“I'd give this strain a solid 4 stars. Try this indica-dominant first thing on a lazy Saturday morning; I guarantee you won't be disappointed. More cerebral than you would expect. I found it to be a nice balance. Don’t forget to turn up the tunes with this one.”
“Yo. This shit is NICE. Like a nice laid back high that lasts for hours!”
“Great Strain to relax after a long day at work. A light taste and a little odor with a powerful mental breeze, gives rise to a stream of senses. Try at the end of the day with good tea.”
“Favorite strain, nugs really are extremely white and solid.”
“She's good to medical use , she's not very good smell but high effect ( good for pain , headache , nausea ) , good for growers beginners . It's a good night marijuana .”

“10 White Label seeds and I got three phenos. The first was a small super-solid-silver christmas tree looking thing that I think may have been a White Ice? Twas very potent, unique skunky smell and taste, strong stone. Finished very early 6-7 weeks. 
Clones kept getting increasingly better. Second pheno was hermie and lacked the same quality as the first, average. The lucky last White Skunk seed turned out to be WHIT...”

“Indicas usually aren't my favorite but this strain is great, it has a smooth sweet flavor mixed with a pungent skunkyness. The high is great, very relaxing and euphoric with a pleasing behind the eyes effect. A good strain to sit on the couch and watch movies to.”
“I recently picked up half gram of concentrate and have used it at night. I enjoy it. I've heard about the flower and how many of my friends like it. I was happy to find it in wax.”
“Great effect, flavor, look. Very good day time weed. Very introspective, great for a bike ride.”
“it was smooth and 😋 delishous... u know the kind of delishousness u smell n then ur mouth starts watering! uplifting and relaxed. was a very enjoyable high! love you Fox Street!!!!!!!”

“I've been trying to find a strain that will get me high, I've developed such a tolerance that I wasn't able to get high but a few grams of white skunk and I'm n feeling better, great for anxiety and depression but will probably couch lock you”

“definitely taste like a skunky citrus weed. Great head high and really helps your muscles relax great after a work out, energetic but still able to enjoy watching TV after a good bath before heading to bed. Average taste unless you really enjoy citrus but great strain over all. THC 28.9”

“not a huge indica guy, but this strain struck me heavy and hard while also giving me a bit of a sativa mind-movement sort of thing, but i was relaxed the whole time. best strain I've had in a long time, especially compared to other indica strains. wouldn't use it if i have to socialize, but i might be able to manage doing some light work with it. dry mouth is the only bummer i really noticed. have plenty of water at ...”
“Knocked me on my ass and let me sleep more than 5 hours for the first time in weeks. Nice.”

“If it smells like a fruit loops that have been sitting in milk and turned soggy, mixed with a skunks rear end, you know it's the wonderful White Skunk. This Strain is incredible for treating Anxiety and pain. It also combats depression nicely. Strain can get quite intense in larger doses. Would Recommend to anyone”
“Made 25 yrs ago better, which I didn't think was possible. My new favorite for sure!”
“Great Strain to relax after a long day at work. A light taste and a little odor with a powerful mental breeze, gives rise to a stream of senses. Try at the end of the day with good tea.”
“Yo. This shit is NICE. Like a nice laid back high that lasts for hours!”

“it's skunk do you really need a description....
Peace! legalize!”
“Really good strain. This make me really sleepy and relaxed. Perfect for chillin' and sleep.”
“Súper relaxed”

“Really nice sativa head high and a little heavy on the eyes, when I first popped the top the smell of grapefruit burnt deep into my nose and it was wonderful would recommend for any daytime user once again I'm an indica kind of guy but will be definitely visiting the wonderful white skunk again.”
“super good stuff man ima be back today too get more of this I was super high an on my Xbox all night lol”
“I have gad and this one made my mind race like crazy. almost hallucinogenic. kept feeling like I was gonna fall into the water.... I was in my living room lol. not my favorite.”
“Bought this in a pre-rolled cone. Good heady high with that nice relaxed body sensation. Tastes good but your throat will feel it after a good sized joint.”
“Awesome strain really light with a heavy effect great for nights”

“and buddy and me just finished legally growing a crop of this. I suffer from chronic pain, as well as neuropathy from two brain surgeries. House of Sun mental side effects from that as well as PTSD excetera. point being is this medication quelled all that for me. it just relaxes me to the bone. The only downside I really notices some dry mouth and a little bit of a headache most like a headband strain. headache dissi...”
